  m_Name: 12_Simulation
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  chapter: 3
  number: 12
  title: Hovercraft Testing
  description: "Test Newton\u2019s laws with real-time free-body diagrams. The player
    adjusts mass, gravity, thrust, and drag as Gizmo guides them through acceleration,
    braking, and controlled collisions. Watch forces balance or unbalance as the
    hovercraft reacts in a futuristic test arena."
  objectives: "Observe how changing forces affect the hovercraft\u2019s motion.\n\nIdentify
    the net force acting on the hovercraft at any moment.\n\nApply Newton\u2019s
    laws to predict acceleration and stopping distance.\n\nComplete each test sequence
    without losing stability."
  scoring: 
  bronzeObjective: 
  silverObjective: 
  goldObjective: 
  timeBonus:
    timeBonuses: []
    lowestScore: 10
  unlockDatas:
  - icon: 1
    name: Level 13 - Lesson
    description: Forces
  - icon: 2
    name: 'Freeplay > Simulation 3 '
    description: Hovercraft Testing
  instructions: '1. Use the arrow buttons beside each parameter (Mass, Gravity, Hover
    Force, Thrust Force, Airbrake Drag) to adjust values.


    2. Press Airbrake
    to apply drag and slow the hovercraft.


    3. Monitor the free-body diagram
    to see all active forces.


    4. Observe how unbalanced forces cause acceleration,
    and balanced forces keep motion constant.


    5. Press End Simulation to finish
    the test and review results.'
